    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Splittown is out of Early Access — bigger and better than ever!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ Achievements to collect.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full controller and Steam Deck support, fully revamped keyboard &amp; mouse hotkeys.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DLC-sized chunk of new content, with multiple new areas and storylines.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tons of new dialogue, animations, gags and music tracks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game hint line and item highlighting via Wimp-Vision™️</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hundreds of bug fixes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117400/extras/008b7ca8ef938f2b8c358ed098538508.poster.avif?t=1760135482\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117400/extras/008b7ca8ef938f2b8c358ed098538508.webm?t=1760135482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117400/extras/008b7ca8ef938f2b8c358ed098538508.mp4?t=1760135482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Splittown is our love letter to the golden age of point-and-click games. Between the sardonic humor, an eclectic soundtrack, and wonderfully crooked art, any fans of early 90s PC gaming will feel right at home. However, it's got a few more tricks up its sleeve: With a world and story that reacts to player choices, Splittown offers a familiar yet fresh take on the classic point-and-click.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117400/extras/bc183b9dd9879cbf11d2a0c107300d5e.poster.avif?t=1760135482\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117400/extras/bc183b9dd9879cbf11d2a0c107300d5e.webm?t=1760135482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117400/extras/bc183b9dd9879cbf11d2a0c107300d5e.mp4?t=1760135482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Splittown embraces the absurdity and whimsy of 90s point-and-clicks, while also drawing from the rich world-building, branching narratives, and player agency of classic CRPGs. Characters you meet aren't there just to be joke dispensers; they have their own motivations, backstories, and arcs. And despite the humor, we've tried to make your actions carry real weight in a world that feels lived-in and authentic. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117400/extras/9d227d9ec6306d7dca8f8c275e095738.poster.avif?t=1760135482\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117400/extras/9d227d9ec6306d7dca8f8c275e095738.webm?t=1760135482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117400/extras/9d227d9ec6306d7dca8f8c275e095738.mp4?t=1760135482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every nook and cranny has been crafted with care over nearly a decade, resulting in a game world brimming with life and interactivity. Whether you’re delving into lore, engaging in unexpected side quests, or simply experimenting with the environment, you’ll find that the world reacts to your actions in surprising ways. It’s a dense and layered world, packed with achievements, collectibles, easter eggs and hidden gags.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117400/extras/21cfb827017868cfc83307f108843152.poster.avif?t=1760135482\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117400/extras/21cfb827017868cfc83307f108843152.webm?t=1760135482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117400/extras/21cfb827017868cfc83307f108843152.mp4?t=1760135482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We've set out to create a narrative filled with genuine moments of suspense, sadness, triumph, and everything in between. The world of Splittown might be absurd on the surface, but for the characters living in it, their struggles and victories are just as real.</p>",
